### Module 3 — Middleware

@base = http://localhost:3000

# ─── Basic echo (with timer + logger middleware running) ─

### GET with route param
GET {{base}}/echo/james?color=blue

### POST with body
POST {{base}}/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{ "message": "hello middleware" }

# ─── Error handling ──────────────────────────────────────

### Triggers AppError (name too short) → 400
GET {{base}}/echo/a

### Triggers unhandled Error → 500
GET {{base}}/crash

### Async error → 503
GET {{base}}/echo/async-error/yes

### Async success
GET {{base}}/echo/async-error/no

# ─── 404 handler ────────────────────────────────────────

### Route that doesn't exist → 404
GET {{base}}/does-not-exist
